OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FConcern over decline in    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FCanada polar bear numbers  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The polar bear population in Canada's  
OL,6, western Hudson Bay has dropped by 27%  
OL,7, in just five years, a report has said. 
OL,9,FA government report estimates that 618 
OL,10,Fanimals lived in the area last year,   
OL,11,Fdown from 842 in 2016.                 
OL,13,FIt says adult female bears and cubs are
OL,14,Fparticularly affected and that climate 
OL,15,Fchange may be a factor in the decline. 
OL,17,FThe Arctic is now warming faster than  
OL,18,Fthe rest of the world, and the sea ice 
OL,19,Fon which bears depend for seal hunting 
OL,20,Fforms later and melts sooner each year.
